items.headline: Welcome to the Umbra Wikia!
items.desc: Umbra is an open world action-RPG taking place in a corrupted world that is falling apart. You are a former soldier, forced to flee the death penalty because of your magic powers. The game is currently being developed by Solarfall Games and was recently Kickstarter funded. This wikia is a collaborative resource for the game and all contributors are welcome.
